Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It is the year 2009.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:39.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\i1}The alien spacecraft that fell\Nto Earth ten years before{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:43.31,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has been reborn as the\Ngigantic battleship "Macross."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.04,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\i1}However, on the day that the Macross\Nwas scheduled to be launched,{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.09,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}its automatic defense system of alien\Norigin suddenly activated itself,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:54.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}firing the main cannon and destroying\Nan unidentified warship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.14,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Humanity was plunged into\Nunavoidable conflict.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:02.53,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Meanwhile, Lynn Minmay, a young girl\Nattending the launch ceremony,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}...and Hikaru Ichijo, a civilian pilot,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.49,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}have also found themselves\Nin the midst of the battle.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:12.26,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(68,124)}SPACE FOLD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:17.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}At this moment, the Macross is\Nmaking its way into space.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:24.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I guess the shock was\Na little too much for him.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is Skull Leader.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I left something on South Ataria Island,\Nand I'm going back to get it.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:40.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Have some other squadron fly\Nescort for the Macross.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What are you picking up?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well... Valkyrie VT-102\Nand its pilot.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}VT-102?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now that you mention it, there was\Nsomething strange about that pilot.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:55.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You think so, too, huh?\NWell, it's not so surprising...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:57.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}...after all, he is a civilian.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}A civilian?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Oh, no!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}No way!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This isn't something I'd want\Na girl to have to see...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's wrong?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:25.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You look like you're shaking.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What?\NWhat is it?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:29.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Don't look!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What?\NWhy not?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just don't look!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, Hikaru!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}How long do you plan on\Nstaying here goofing off?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Aliens have the hots for you, huh?\NTalk about bad luck!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:02.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It can do that, too?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's going on?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Handy, huh?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:06.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is control.\NWe are now engaging main thrusters.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Prepare for retrieval of Valkyrie squadrons.\NAll units, move into landing positions.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is Mountain Three.\NFollowing landing line.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're cleared to land.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hayase, is the Valkyrie\Nretrieval completed?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Just a moment, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:40.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}All that's left is Major Focker and\Nthe civilian pilot in VT-102.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Knowing Focker, there's nothing\Nto worry about.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Vanessa, where are ARMD-I and ARMD-II?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They're nearly at the rendezvous point\Nand currently decelerating.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I estimate contact in 20 minutes.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:56.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Very good.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Claudia, how are we doing?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Right on schedule, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But it's strange, isn't it, Captain?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:08.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If the enemy fleet can launch that\Nkind of attack from orbit,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}then why aren't they firing on us now?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, that's bothering you too?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They may be toying with us.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:23.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You can't be serious!\NToying with us?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's just a feeling.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Pay it no mind.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!\NI'm not going to go to the Macross!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:42.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Idiot! If you take her back to\Nthe island, you'll be risking her life!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And you call yourself a man?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Um, my aunt and uncle are on\Nthe island in the shelter.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:55.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If they're in the shelter, they'll be fine!\NEven if this does turn into an all-out war.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:58.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But I really would like to go\Nback to the island...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Once the fighting's over,\NI'll take you back personally.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That is what really\Nworries me!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, what he means is...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is Skull Leader!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Did you find what you'd left behind?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yeah, the enemy had him scared so bad,\Nhe was falling over himself!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I was not!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, this is the civilian?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That would explain why he\Ndidn't know anything.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hey, what's with the old lady?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:22.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}"Old lady"?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}She's the flight control\nofficer of the Macross.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}So, even Hikaru thinks she\Nlooks like an old lady?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:37.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Major Focker!\NI will expect a thorough explanation{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}as to why you let a civilian\Nboard VT-102.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Ooh, scary!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}And you, Mr. Ichijo!\NThis isn't over for you by a long shot!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's her problem?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Maybe you should just apologize.\NPeople like her can be pretty scary.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I'm comin' in!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Requesting instructions\N...old lady!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Roger. We'd appreciate it if you didn't\Nkill yourself when you land.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Retrieval of Reguld platoons\Nis now in progress.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:27.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Only half of them are unharmed?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:28.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, sir.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What's the enemy ship doing?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It's currently ascending through the\Nplanet's upper atmosphere.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}They appear be trying to rendezvous\Nwith the space fleet from earlier.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Orders, sir?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}It would be simple to shoot them down,\Nbut that ship interests me.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:46.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}If they enter orbit, there's a possibility\Nthey will execute a fold and escape.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Yes, I know.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}We'll have to launch a containment attack\Nbefore they can join up with the others.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}All ships, prepare to fire!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}But why do you have to kill each other?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}That's what war is.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I just can't understand the military...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You did some shooting yourself,\Nthough, didn't you?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I never imagined something\Nlike that could be inside.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Something like that...{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Huh?\NSomething like what?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}What?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Hang on!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, here we are.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai!\NWhat's wrong with you?!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sempai!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Thank you, Sempai!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, I mean, if we left something\Nlike this on the battlefield,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}it would just get in the way.\NSo I, uh, had it stashed away.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This is the plane from the air show\Nthis morning, isn't it?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.47,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Rendezvous with ARMD-I and\NARMD-II is complete.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.22,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now moving into docking position.\NAll hands to emergency stations.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Well, I've got work to do.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:50.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You two, stay right here. If you start\Nwandering around, you'll get lost.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}This ship is massive.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Now moving into docking alignment.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}The enemy fleet appears to be regrouping.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Very well.\NFire a barrage between the fleet and the battleship!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}I don't care about the smaller ships,\Nbut do NOT hit that battleship.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Understood!\NFiring will now commence!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:29.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Target the enemy fleet!\NAim wide of the battleship!{\b0}
